{"tid":2119298,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"健身舞蹈業界轟政府人禍爆疫","createTime":"2020-07-22T04:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T04:47:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9178fb6c98a4c72b91e8284db9eb3f372df0074d","tid":2119298,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200722/M6CQXIOZP6WIRB6JJTE4U7D7NQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FM6CQXIOZP6WIRB6JJTE4U7D7NQ%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB3JTAtm2oKGHsrawk8oVPbs%3D&h=a89c0477\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200722%2FM6CQXIOZP6WIRB6JJTE4U7D7NQ%2F&h=47b31b6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200722/M6CQXIOZP6WIRB6JJTE4U7D7NQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n健身舞蹈業界轟政府人禍爆疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Taauom3q8HtjlhHf5hpKIRpRoGk=/640x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RN5B3DEYERX2OBTHFPMYZU2SAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTaauom3q8HtjlhHf5hpKIRpRoGk%3D%2F640x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRN5B3DEYERX2OBTHFPMYZU2SAE.jpg&h=74fb76be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n健身、武術及舞蹈業界人士昨開記招要求政府向業界賠償。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】健身中心及遊戲機中心等12類場所須繼續停業，昨日多名健身、武術及舞蹈業界人士召開聯合記者會，批評政府防疫把關不力，釀成第三波爆發的「人禍」。業界促盡快落實第三輪防疫抗疫基金，並對業界作合理賠償，使業界可以有及時應急金額渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：入境免檢疫種禍 口罩令太遲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「應急錢一啲都應唔到急」<br />\n<br />\n泰拳健體中心負責人柯尊鼎表示，由1月至今，生計大受影響，然而政府對不同規模的拳館劃一補貼10萬元資助，未有幫助業界紓困。許多。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n舞蹈中心負責人蕭翊深認為，第三波爆發的客觀因素是入境人流，政府把關不力，不是業界造成，但政府卻將責任推卸予市民。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「保就業、10萬元補貼到𠵱家我都收唔到。」。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"40ecdd365e7ac9835a6980da0414760307bc6c4d","tid":2119298,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"政府應該賠償損失"}]}